&lt;hr/&gt;
&lt;p&gt;First of all, I want to touch on the two fundamental concepts of working with files:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Pipes</title><link>https://biriukov.dev/docs/fd-pipe-session-terminal/2-pipes/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://biriukov.dev/docs/fd-pipe-session-terminal/2-pipes/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="pipes"&gt;
